name: Lauren WK - Painting #2
description:
While I am for the most part a photographer, I do sometimes use my own photos to create stencils which I then spray paint onto canvas. Each of these will be a 1/1 edition of a unique physical painting that lives somewhere out there in the real world. I used some of my stencils multiple times but each painting was a unique color scheme and the stencil painting process itself created a one of a kind  painting each time a stencil was used. This is the second and last version of this stencil.

The person who buys this NFT will receive an NFT of the photo this stencil was created from as well. I will send it to the same wallet that buys the painting as soon as I see the sale.
